{"tid":1579262,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"作為曼迷..今晚竟然識到位利物浦女手足！！！","createTime":"2019-09-18T13:24:26.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-25T18:03:09.000Z","uid":8968,"like":33,"dislike":11,"uniUserReply":19,"replies":[{"pid":"79deaf0fd5c5ba4c0cab13cc728ee29aefd93873","tid":1579262,"uid":8968,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-18T13:24:26.000Z","msg":"話說今晚球迷大和解<br />\n我就著左件最新曼連迪洛夫波衫去左維園<br />\n最初行去比較多曼手足個邊，屌<br />\n女都冇條 得班死毒撚<br />\n咁就膽粗粗行去其他隊地頭<br />\n行到利個邊 個心勁撚淆<br />\n<br />\n但係天使就係你最軟弱時候出現<br />\n有位著利波衫女手足<br />\n雖然冇喜般咁可愛<br />\n但著波衫都好似幾大波<br />\n<br />\n佢同我講「加油 YNWA」<br />\n我...<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e320ae99b5e6765d732ff34844827eec2874a072","tid":1579262,"uid":117906,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-18T13:25:06.000Z","msg":"<strong><span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">全球響應「929全球集會抗赤納粹」</span></span></strong><br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">全世界一齊對準極權！</span></span></strong><br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1577380\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1577380</a><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/hWqVmOV.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FhWqVmOV.jpg&h=075c7745&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/n1tov9s.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fn1tov9s.png&h=0af09f95&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"074d836620f4af2dca7526194e6721fc67f95669","tid":1579262,"uid":3747,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-18T13:26:14.000Z","msg":"曼狗聽日咪豬波囉"},{"pid":"b0482cc18ce93ba58887e164585b2a6bed77e459","tid":1579262,"uid":42246,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-09-18T13:26:31.000Z","msg":"有個女行迷係幾勁 睇直播"},{"pid":"63889c64348d668c4514d7967c276af369b62631","tid":1579262,"uid":8968,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"074d836620f4af2dca75